>
>
> #######################################################################
>
> ===========
> 3) The Code
> ===========
>
>
> Launch a telnet client and connect to the victim host on port 6144.
> Now press RETURN about 10 times or more.
> Disconnect, reconnect again and press RETURN.
> The remote host should be crashed.
